      <title>CVC 和 ADIA 再次出价 54 亿英镑收购 Hargreaves Lansdown</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-18/cvc-adia-make-fresh-5-4-billion-bid-for-hargreaves-lansdown</link>
