    <item>
      <title>南非再次选举西里尔·拉马福萨为总统</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-06-18/south-africa-reelects-cyril-ramaphosa-as-president</link>
      <description><![CDATA[就在西里尔·拉马福萨再次当选南非总统几个小时前，他所在的非洲人国民大会与亲商的反对党达成了权力分享协议。其他政党支持现任总统连任五年，作为交换，他将获得内阁职位和立法机构的关键职位。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-06-18/south-africa-reelects-cyril-ramaphosa-as-president</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 18 Jun 2024 13:01:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>加拿大保持银行资本水平稳定，称家庭债务风险稳定</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-18/canada-holds-bank-capital-levels-steady-says-household-debt-risk-is-stable</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大金融监管机构维持该国最大银行的资本要求不变，表明官员们认为这些银行的资产负债表足够强劲，能够抵御经济动荡。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-18/canada-holds-bank-capital-levels-steady-says-household-debt-risk-is-stable</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 18 Jun 2024 12:52:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Stora 首席执行官表示，该公司将投资 1 亿欧元用于木质电动汽车电池</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-18/stora-enso-hel-sterv-invests-in-lignin-ev-batteries-ceo-hans-sohlstrom-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据斯道拉恩索公司首席执行官称，该公司将投资约 1 亿欧元（1.1 亿美元）用于一项开创性项目，利用木材制造电动汽车电池，为目前在中国生产的零部件提供替代品]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-18/stora-enso-hel-sterv-invests-in-lignin-ev-batteries-ceo-hans-sohlstrom-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 18 Jun 2024 12:52:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>达斯称印度通胀正在以“非常”缓慢的速度缓和</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-18/india-s-inflation-moderating-at-a-very-slow-pace-das-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度储备银行行长沙克提坎塔·达斯周二表示，印度的通胀持续居高不下，因此央行讨论改变货币政策立场还为时过早。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-18/india-s-inflation-moderating-at-a-very-slow-pace-das-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 18 Jun 2024 12:52:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>南非股市飙升暗示投票后市场情绪出现转变</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-18/usd-zar-south-africa-stocks-rand-surge-on-government-of-national-unity-gnu</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非股市基准指数今年涨幅最大，表明在经历了三年来最长的单日资金流出后，投资者对该国股市的看法开始转为乐观。兰特和政府债券价格飙升。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-18/usd-zar-south-africa-stocks-rand-surge-on-government-of-national-unity-gnu</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 18 Jun 2024 10:59:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
